《'''奔腾年代'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Halt and Catch Fire'''''}}）是一部由{{link-en|克里斯多福·坎特韋爾|Christopher Cantwell (filmmaker)}}和克里斯托弗·C·罗杰斯（Christopher C. Rogers）创造的美国[[时代剧|时代剧]]，于2014年6月1日在[[AMC_(电视频道)|AMC]]首播，2017年10月14日播放完畢。<ref>{{cite web|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|title=TCA: AMC Picks Up ‘Halt & Catch Fire’ & ‘Turn’ To Series|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/07/tca-amc-picks-up-halt-catch-fire-turn-to-series/|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=July 26, 2014|accessdate=August 7, 2013|archive-date=2014-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140624120414/http://www.deadline.com/2013/07/tca-amc-picks-up-halt-catch-fire-turn-to-series/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=AMC Drama ‘Halt and Catch Fire’ to Bow June 1 After ‘Mad Men’ Finale|url=http://variety.com/2014/tv/news/amc-drama-halt-and-catch-fire-to-premiere-june-1-after-mad-men-finale-1201125754/|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=March 5, 2014|accessdate=March 5, 2014|archive-date=2014-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308213659/http://variety.com/2014/tv/news/amc-drama-halt-and-catch-fire-to-premiere-june-1-after-mad-men-finale-1201125754/|dead-url=no}}</ref>首播集的预览于2014年5月公开。电视剧背景设置在1980年代早期，从虚构的知情者角度描绘了一幅[[家用电脑|家用电脑革命]]的图景。电视剧的标题引用了[[机器语言|机器语言]]中可以令电脑停止工作的指令{{tsl|en|Halt and Catch Fire|Halt and Catch Fire (计算机指令)|Halt and Catch Fire}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvline.com/2014/06/01/halt-and-catch-fire-series-premiere-recap/ |title=''Halt and Catch Fire'': Does AMC's New Drama Compute? |publisher=TVLine |first=Kimberly |last=Roots |date=June 1, 2014 |accessdate=June 2, 2014 |archive-date=2015-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150903121814/http://tvline.com/2014/06/01/halt-and-catch-fire-series-premiere-recap/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

