== 制作和发展 ==
[[AMC_(电视频道)|AMC]]于2012年11月订购了《奔腾年代》的试播集。<ref name="deadline">{{cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/11/amc-orders-period-drama-pilots-from-craig-silversteinbarry-josephson-mark-johnson/ |title=AMC Orders Period Drama Pilots From Craig Silverstein/Barry Josephson, Mark Johnson |publisher=Deadline.com |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |date=November 27, 2012 |accessdate=May 24, 2014 |archive-date=2014-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140525200447/http://www.deadline.com/2012/11/amc-orders-period-drama-pilots-from-craig-silversteinbarry-josephson-mark-johnson/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>试播集的制作于2013年4月在[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]][[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]开始。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fanbolt.com/amc-set-to-film-new-pilot-halt-catch-fire-in-atlanta-this-month/ |title=AMC Set To Film New Pilot ‘Halt & Catch Fire’ In Atlanta This Month |publisher=FanBolt |date=April 8, 2013 |accessdate=May 24, 2014 |archive-date=2014-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140525233840/http://www.fanbolt.com/amc-set-to-film-new-pilot-halt-catch-fire-in-atlanta-this-month/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> AMC于2013年7月宣布已将《奔腾年代》订购成剧。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2013/07/26/amc-halt-catch-fire-turn/ |title=AMC greenlights drama series 'Halt & Catch Fire' and 'Turn' |work=Entertainment Weekly |first=Dan |last=Snierson |date=July 26, 2013 |accessdate=May 24, 2014 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714090553/http://insidetv.ew.com/2013/07/26/amc-halt-catch-fire-turn/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>电视剧由克里斯托弗·坎特维尔和克里斯托弗·C·罗杰斯创造，<ref name="deadline"/>由乔纳森·利斯科出任[[節目統籌|節目統籌]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/07/jonathan-lisco-inks-overall-deal-with-amc/ |title=Jonathan Lisco Inks Overall Deal With AMC |publisher=Deadline.com |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |date=July 30, 2013 |accessdate=May 24, 2014 |archive-date=2014-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140510102410/http://www.deadline.com/2013/07/jonathan-lisco-inks-overall-deal-with-amc/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

